            YMR089C make up the mitochondrial adenosine
            <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">triphosphatase</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">m-AAA</ENAMEX>) protease <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">complex</ENAMEX>, which is
